{"tid":277922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【爭取獨立】西班牙加泰羅尼亞 10月公投決定前途","createTime":"2017-06-10T04:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T13:09:49.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"194c5adf804f8a7e6efe2c0f8c3d6f5386e60922","tid":277922,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:52:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170609/56806206\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170609%2F56806206&d=I2c5v6%2BUs4GnJ2gdj2U%2BBYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=0c958fe4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170609%2F56806206&h=32858042\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170609/56806206</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.centrocampista.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Catalonia_Is_Not_Spain-e1334133003101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.centrocampista.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F04%2FCatalonia_Is_Not_Spain-e1334133003101.jpg&h=3d4efd6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西班牙加泰羅尼亞自治區政府宣佈，今年10月1日舉行獨立公投，料會遇到中央政府阻力。<br />\n<br />\n自治區主席普伊格登莫尼特（Carles Puigdemont）於首府巴塞隆拿發表電視講話，宣佈公投題目為「你希望加泰羅尼亞以共和國形式成為獨立國家嗎？」他指日期和題目都在馬德里政府拒絕合作下，由他們單方面決定，「我們已提供許多方案，但一律被拒絕」，形容公投雖勢在必行，但仍希望與馬德里對話。<br />\n<br />\n近期民調顯示，49%加泰羅尼亞人反對獨立、44%支持，近3/4受訪者希望舉行公投。當地人口約750萬，佔全西班牙約1/10，經濟收入卻是全國兩成，加上獨特的語言、文化及歷史背景，令當地人對西班牙產生離心。<br />\n<br />\n加泰羅尼亞自治區政府曾於2014年舉行獨立公投，但西班牙憲法法院將公投列為非法，令公投只能以非正式形式舉行，投票率約42%，當中逾80%支持獨立。<br />\n法新社"},{"pid":"d8689dd9e81c3eaf108e41f8b7d20a09ad024e01","tid":277922,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:55:25.000Z","msg":"加泰係西班牙不可分裂嘅一部分<br />\n加泰自古以來屬於西班牙"},{"pid":"ce378041031e71d8b51c5e859a335e53c28d1108","tid":277922,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:32:21.000Z","msg":"如果西班牙政府唔承認, 又咪一樣無用"},{"pid":"f7376b09cd4c0dab476c88ef04243399c62fbe01","tid":277922,"uid":8515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:39:37.000Z","msg":"以前高登有個加泰仔，唔知有冇份投呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92cfdfd184f5d0c56fb5cd28c709219a09c8cca7","tid":277922,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:47:30.000Z","msg":"3年內由80%跌到49%? （雖然只係民調）"},{"pid":"e4e1adbb36bdb3ba19d5c97647e03708a8c01d30","tid":277922,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3年內由80%跌到<span style=\"color: red;\">44</span>%? （雖然只係民調）</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7b189a64383d739da093491b6a1a48c7fb2667fc","tid":277922,"uid":36715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T13:09:49.000Z","msg":"外國勢力介入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n英國忘我之心不死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}